                "html": "While it's true that most mohrgs seem to rise from the corpses of humanoid killers, the capacity to murder is not limited to humanoids. Mohrgs of other sorts could certainly exist\u2014as long as they come from a society that has the capacity not only to judge and execute, but also to harbor murder within their hearts."
            }
